parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the vehicle to lose traction, leading to loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The ABS light illuminates on the dashboard
the brakes make a grinding or clicking sound
the brake pedal travels to the floor
the vehicle surges forward or fishtails
and the brakes fail to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal travels to the floor
the brakes make a grinding or clicking sound
and the vehicle fails to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal travels to the floor
the brakes make a grinding or clicking sound
and the vehicle fails to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: the vehicle has difficulty shifting gears

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
and the vehicle has difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Slipping or Failure to Engage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or failure to engage can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or shift into neutral without warning, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or fails to engage
the transmission shifts into neutral without warning
the RPMs rise to high levels
the vehicle is unable to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission downshifting or entering limp mode can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or shift into neutral without warning, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the transmission shifts into neutral without warning
the RPMs rise to high levels
the vehicle is unable to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure to Shift or Engage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission failure to shift or engage can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or shift into neutral without warning, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the transmission shifts into neutral without warning
the RPMs rise to high levels
the vehicle is unable to accelerate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling can cause loss of power steering and power brakes, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: loss of power steering and power brakes

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission problems can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
Cooling system issues can cause engine damage, overheating, and loss of power.
Electrical system problems can cause engine stalling, loss of power, and accidents.
Sensor failures can cause engine stalling, loss of power, and accidents.
